{"tid":1475646,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"事實查核症候群（Fact-check syndrome）","createTime":"2019-08-15T14:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T14:21:46.000Z","uid":179547,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6994b5c15ca99d94fedf2e9675e70bb533291d69","tid":1475646,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"事實查核症候群（英語：Fact-check syndrome）又稱為事實查核情結、事實查核綜合症，是一種心理學現象，是指被害者以超理性方式對待不同資訊，凡事講求絕對真實，甚至對與加害者相關的資訊亦持超理性、求真態度，同情加害者，認同加害者的某些觀點和想法，甚至反過來為加害者澄清的一種情結。這些情感被認為是過分理性的，甚至是帶有潔癖的。<br />\n<br />\n事實查核症候群常見於反建制群眾，尤以連登討論區網民為甚。他們認為絕對真實是世間真理，因此對事實查核樂此不疲，尤其是針對親中共陣型的資訊。"},{"pid":"4d7e3e73e8ef344fc670fb0da509484371ac128c","tid":1475646,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a7dc410925add02d51e9f4573689c5f303dc2d","tid":1475646,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbcb04cf8b9b6ada6ad011c191bb008f6c7d0051","tid":1475646,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17d51f7e67094191a76b8da8605ae3fa21e4c31","tid":1475646,"uid":98542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKkQXjZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKkQXjZ.jpg&h=0c5b3ebf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22f65a70d013e33992b260ef088b919b53b71d19","tid":1475646,"uid":108687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6994b5c15ca99d94fedf2e9675e70bb533291d69","tid":1475646,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"事實查核症候群（英語：Fact-check syndrome）又稱為事實查核情結、事實查核綜合症，是一種心理學現象，是指被